<HL>
   Business Brief -- Inco Ltd.:
   Lazare Kaplan Partnership
   Involves Ghana Diamonds
</HL>
<DATE>
08/27/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A4
</SO>
